<plot>This documentary "making-of" short is a detailed behind-the-scenes look at the creation and filming of the insect-like alien villains of the motion picture "Starship Troopers". This film is divided into five sections, each devoted to a different creature: the Warrior Bug, the Tanker Bug, the Hopper Bug, the Plasma Bug, and the Brain Bug.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?294874</url></doc>
